  (6, 'en', 'Evp\\Bundle\\TicketBundle\\Entity\\Event', 'description', '1', '<p>The Conference Board of Vilnius has established the Centre for Business Innovation (CBI) as a five-year initiative to help bring about major improvements in firm-level business innovation in Vilnius, Lithuania.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 2015 Business Innovation Summit explored the real-life challenges and opportunities for innovation within firms and tangible solutions. Industry professionals and expert speakers took part in delegate-expert sharing sessions, giving participants the insights and tools to increase the speed at which their organizations can generate new ideas, products, services, and processes.</p>'),
